<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1918-12-12T08:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1918-12-12T08:00:00-05:00" n="207" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d207">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">763.72119/2968: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Commission to Negotiate
                                    Peace</gloss> to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                                    State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                                </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-12-12T13:00:00+00:00">December 12, 1918—1 p.m.</date>
                                <lb/> [Received 2:30 p.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>7. From <persName corresp="#p_GJC1">Grew</persName>. Will you please
                            request the consuls throughout the Allied and neutral countries and
                            those countries bordering the Mediterranean to transmit to the American
                            Mission copies of recent and all future reports dealing with the
                            political situation or with any economic situation of sufficient
                            magnitude to have political significance. This request is made in order
                            that we may have at hand here the information on which to predicate
                            comments, criticisms and the like in regard to existing conditions.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Am</hi>[<hi rend="smallcaps">erican</hi>] <hi rend="smallcaps">Mission</hi>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>